OL,3,CChris Kamara raises awareness of
OL,4,Capraxia at event in Manchester
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent
OL,7,FVictoria Grimes spoke to Chris Kamara
OL,8,Fat an event in Manchester
OL,10,FFormer footballer Chris Kamara has
OL,11,Fbeen recalling how he "suffered in
OL,12,Fsilence" with speech problems for
OL,13,Falmost two years before he was
OL,14,Fdiagnosed with a thyroid problem.
OL,16,FThe TV pundit was eventually found to
OL,17,Fbe suffering from apraxia, after
OL,18,Fviewers noticed him slurring his words
OL,19,Fon air.
