OL,3,CChris Kamara raises awareness of
OL,4,Capraxia at event in Manchester
OL,6,FChris has been raising awareness of
OL,7,Fthe condition at an event in
OL,8,FManchester and speaking about how the
OL,9,Fcondition has affected him.
OL,11,F"You think exactly the same, but then
OL,12,Fthe passage from the brain to the
OL,13,Fmouth is either non-existent or
OL,14,Fintermittent."
OL,16,FChris is supporting the campaign group
OL,17,FMikey's Wish which aims to make speech
OL,18,Fand language therapy available to all
OL,19,Fchildren.
