OL,3,CChris Kamara raises awareness of
OL,4,Capraxia at event in Manchester
OL,6,F6-year old Zach Wilson has had speech
OL,7,Fand language therapy to treat his
OL,8,Fapraxia, and it's made a big
OL,9,Fdifference to his speech. But it's
OL,10,Fcome at a cost. Zach's parents have
OL,11,Fhad to find 10 thousand pounds for his
OL,12,Fprivate treatment.
OL,14,FSteve Jamieson, CEO of the Royal
OL,15,FCollege of Speech and Language
OL,16,FTherapists, says there is a "massive
OL,17,Fproblem because of the shortage of
OL,18,Fspeech and language therapists" and
OL,19,Fthe organisation is calling for more
OL,20,Ftraining for therapists.
