OL,6,FThe event was also attended by the
OL,7,FMayor of Greater Manchester, Andy
OL,8,FBurnham, who told the audience that
OL,9,FSpeech and Language Therapy should be
OL,10,Fseen as a "core, essential service
OL,11,Fthat needs to be fully funded and
OL,12,Fproperly organised."
